---
title: Garlic & Herb Parmesan Beef Rissoles with Fries, Caramelised Onion & Apple Salad
description: Give rissoles a herby hit with garlic and herb seasoning, plus Parmesan for an easy flavour boost. With potato fries and a tangy Italian-dressed salad, this meal shines a whole new light on a tried-and-true dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/garlic-herb-parmesan-beef-rissoles-959b787b.jpg
